🧠 What is Debugging?

Debugging means:

👉 Finding, analyzing, and fixing errors in your code

```text
Bug → Identify → Fix → Test → Done
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 Why Debugging is Important?

Without debugging:

❌ App crashes
❌ Hard to fix bugs
❌ Poor performance

With debugging:

✔ Faster development
✔ Better code quality
✔ Easier maintenance

